<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/nov/04/">&#x27a0;</a> November 4, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="on-the-hour" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://onthehour.info/">On The Hour</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The iconic BBC radio series (which gave way to The Day Today) finally gets a full CD release (including bonus material, such as Chris Morris&#8217;s fantastic flexidisc for Select Magazine).  Subscribe to the podcast for snippets of genius.</p>

