    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="doctor-who-steven-moffat" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/s4/news/latest/080520_news_01">Doctor Who - Steven Moffat Takes Charge</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>This is amazingly good news.  Steven Moffat (writer of Coupling and Press Gang, as well as the best episodes of &#8220;new&#8221; Doctor Who) is taking over as lead writer.  I&#8217;m giddy at the prospect of what&#8217;s to come.</p>

