        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7367385.stm">BBC NEWS | Jazz legend Lyttelton dies at 86</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Man, this is sad news.  Humph&#8217;s impeccably innocent delivery of a filthy &#8220;double&#8221; entendre on &#8220;I&#8217;m Sorry I Haven&#8217;t a Clue&#8221; had me in hysterics many a time.  He will be missed.</p>

